ZH: 农民是农村的主要劳动力。
EN: Farmers are the main workforce in rural areas.

ZH: 农民种庄稼，赶牲口。
EN: Farmers plant crops and herd animals.

ZH: 农民熟练地耕田，施肥。
EN: Farmers skillfully plow the fields and fertilize the land.

ZH: 农民在田间忙碌一整天。
EN: Farmers work tirelessly in the fields all day.

ZH: 农民们从清晨开始忙碌，直到日落。
EN: Farmers start working from early morning and continue until sunset.

ZH: 农民向市场供应新鲜蔬菜和水果。
EN: Farmers supply fresh vegetables and fruits to the market.

ZH: 农民是建设社会主义农村的中坚力量。
EN: Farmers are the backbone of building socialist rural areas.

ZH: 农民在困难时期展现出了无尽的坚韧。
EN: Farmers have shown endless resilience in times of hardship.

ZH: 农民是国家的宝贵财富。
EN: Farmers are a valuable asset to the country.

ZH: 农民是实现农村振兴的基石。
EN: Farmers are the cornerstone of rural revitalization.

ZH: 农民在种植季节里辛苦劳作。
EN: Farmers work hard during the planting season.

ZH: 农民们互相帮助，共同致富。
EN: Farmers help each other to achieve prosperity together.

ZH: 农民在田间忙碌，一声不吭。
EN: Farmers work silently in the fields.

ZH: 农民对土地充满感情。
EN: Farmers have a strong attachment to the land.

ZH: 农民传承着种田的技艺。
EN: Farmers pass down the skills of farming.

ZH: 农民勤劳朴实，为家乡增光添彩。
EN: Farmers are hardworking and contribute to the glory of their hometown.

ZH: 农民用自己的双手创造出美好生活。
EN: Farmers create a better life with their own hands.

ZH: 农民拼搏奋斗，不畏艰辛。
EN: Farmers struggle and persevere without fear of hardships.

ZH: 农民是农村的脊梁。
EN: Farmers are the backbone of the countryside.
